replies.body:
1. Restart the client and attempt to access the Hextech Hub again. If you still receive a blank page it's likely due to your network not establishing a stable connection to the Hub;

2. [Troubleshoot your connectivity issues.](https://support.riotgames.com/hc/en-us/articles/201752664-Troubleshooting-Connection-Issues)

